## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible causes of resentment in marriage. Additionally, the information is subject to the perspectives and expertise of the authors of the sources used. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.